For the people are confused on how to share stickers from a pedestal which is a new mechanic on VRChat with VRChat+ so First Step is to own VRChat+ but if you do already then. Go to Settings, Comfort & Safety, then click on Allow Pedestal Sharing & Direct Sharing and to see the Pedestal also click on View Pedestal From to Everyone or Friends.  You want to get some stickers from friends or others on VRChat then you would also have to turn on Accept Sharing From to everyone or Friends. You're Welcome.